@page "/orders-and-payments"

<div class="container py-5">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-4 pb-2 border-bottom border-3">Orders & Payments</h2>

    <!-- Order Info -->
    <div class="card shadow-sm p-4 mb-4">
        <h4 class="mb-3">🛒 Placing an Order</h4>
        <p>Ordering from Bob Kart is simple and secure. Just add your favourite items to the cart, head to checkout, and follow the steps to complete your purchase.</p>
        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
            @*<li class="list-group-item">After placing your order, you’ll receive a confirmation email instantly.</li>*@
            <li class="list-group-item">We’ll send another email with tracking details once your order is shipped.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Payment Info -->
    <div class="card shadow-sm p-4 mb-4">
        <h4 class="mb-3">💳 Payment Options</h4>
        <p>We accept all major UK and international payment methods:</p>
        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <li class="list-group-item">Credit/Debit Cards: Visa, MasterCard, American Express</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Digital Wallets: Apple Pay, Google Pay, PayPal</li>
            <li class="list-group-item">Buy Now, Pay Later: Klarna, Clearpay (on orders over £30)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">All transactions are encrypted and secure. You’ll never be charged more than what’s shown at checkout.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Order Issues -->
    <div class="card shadow-sm p-4 mb-4">
        <h4 class="mb-3">❗ Problems with Your Order?</h4>
        <p>If there's an issue with your order or payment, <a href="/contact" class="link-primary text-decoration-underline">contact our support team</a> right away. We're here to help!</p>
    </div>
</div>